[22-Apr-12] ** Change log

Some major bugs have been fixed for the 22-Apr-12 release, it is important that you redownload in order to get the most out of the bots!

This is a compilation of all of the most functional RuneScape macros and bots. 

I take no credit for any of the bots featured in my compilation.

Upon the completion of your download, please make sure to seed so my compilation can be shared with many more players.

Thank you for your contribution, and I hope you enjoy these programs.

Stay tuned, and bookmark my profile for consistent updates!
